  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6718221/" class="title-link">罗志田老师的自序</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6718221"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/redbreast/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u29449961-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/redbreast/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">时间与玫瑰</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-06-27"
      class="main-meta">2014-06-27 08:22:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6718221_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  自序   很多年前，曾对一位研究中国近代史的朋友说，近代一段，可以六字总结，即满汉中西新旧。那是读大学本科时产生的一种朦胧感觉，年轻时不知轻重，故敢出大言而不惭。彼时我的学术自定位是研究中美关系史，这是说别人的领域，多少有些外行看热闹的味道。后来不知不觉中，自...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6718221/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6718221_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6718221_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





